<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>514</hymn_number>
<title>KAWLRAM HLA CH514</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw Kawlram zungzal hmun, Kan pipu ro si ca'h upat u si, Ram pumpi cu kan
 nun dongh tiang khamh u si, Kan ram kan vawlei kanmah ta a si, Kan ram,
 vawlei, Lungnge tein kan ram ca, Tuan zungzal u si, Kan ram a si, Ram
 sungmi.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>